    "Expandability with Human Inputs: The capability of the framework to incorporate expert feedback and real-world developments into the scenario generation process, allowing for continuous improvement and adaptation to emerging cyber threats.",
    "Case studyIn this case study, we included listings depicting scenarios created by Large Language Models (LLMs), following the design outlined in Figure 1.",
